0,"uid":37058,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:26:14.000Z","msg":"立即罷工啦仆街 等到2月你地中晒招想唔罷都無得簡"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:32:08.000Z","msg":"我先前成功推算中共火化死者壓低因肺炎死亡人數<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1836132/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1836132/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n我現在推算2月香港開始爆發<br />\n醫護2月先罷工唔會有民意支持<br />\n<br />\n<ins>要做就趁香港中招者未發病時做</ins>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:30:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e178c508c0d2d23edb721247f100ac9931beb1eb","tid":1838540,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:31:23.000Z","msg":"推 真心On9"},{"pid":"e9a121b31d0ebbff17b5d3bb2d6b6a19d388c56b","tid":1838540,"uid":197213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:34:13.000Z","msg":"即時罷工！！<br />\n<br />\n咁撚忙，要有少數人罷就已經可以癱瘓成個system逼埋人同你一齊罷<br />\n<br />\n重申：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">立即罷工</span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"86ef6d3bf4555a1a239b14f275ef837b1ebeba49","tid":1838540,"uid":263018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:35:11.000Z","msg":"有道理"},{"pid":"93d24efc6f1b540ce8831e8fb693f38218755e35","tid":1838540,"uid":36920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:16:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"342a5a521cae116ac40b992514473a60f491596e","tid":1838540,"uid":105352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:17:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d6d25af3a41e688fc39089a2e5b3a981b156683","tid":1838540,"uid":277363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:31:22.000Z","msg":"呢樣絕對唔洗擔心<br />\n係咁放支那人落黎，佢地死係第一線<br />\n仲咁努力返工，可以怪邊個?<br />\n要大愛要捨身取義，可以怪邊個?"},{"pid":"dd050e85f4689ed721082f7219d37dcdd8315ea6","tid":1838540,"uid":308494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c9668a04e860923bad639bbde42ba8e89ed3dfb","tid":1838540,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:14:34.000Z","msg":"醫護現在的方案係28號先開大會<ins>傾罷工</ins>,可能拉到<ins>2月中</ins>先罷到工<br />\n問題係現在一車車支那人湧去公院,到2月中若已經社區大爆發(大量香港人受感染),黃絲都唔會支持罷工<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係戰爭上掌握時期比萬全準備重要</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T12:08:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30af66ff865b80a2671bc4216d3897d1502fcdc3","tid":1838540,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:14:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n袁國勇所講的同我推算接近一樣</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thelancet.com/pb-assets/Lancet/pdfs/S0140673620301549.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thelancet.com%2Fpb-assets%2FLancet%2Fpdfs%2FS0140673620301549.pdf&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX5mCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=c6ddc96e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thelancet.com/pb-assets/Lancet/pdfs/S0140673620301549.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n袁國勇給大的重要訊息<br />\n<br />\n&quot;From Professor KY Yuen:<br />\n<br />\n1)the key issue here is a VERY high attack rate in family cluster, 83% in family members who have been in Wuhan; this shows that 2019-nCoV can be a highly infectious virus.<br />\n2. HK/Macau or other world cities could easily become another Wuhan or another 2003 Hong Kong.<br />\n3. The next few days (incubation period 3 to 6 days in our family cluster) could be the last window of opportunity to stop the infection from spreading by silently infected mainlanders that crossed the border into HK/Macau SAR.<br />\n4. patients can be afebrile at the time of presentation, despite having radiological changes of viral pneumonia. They can still be shedding virus as evident by positive RT-PCR in respiratory secretions. This makes the control by case recognition very difficult.<br />\n5. person-to-person transmission can occur in hospital and home setting with intercity spread (ie, from Wuhan to HK/Macau).<br />\n6. We should advocate &ldquo;universal masking outside home&rdquo; and &ldquo;frequent alcoholic handrub&rdquo; now before it is TOO LATE. There should be extension of Chinese New Year holiday till the situation is stable to prevent returning mainland students bringing virus into schools or universities.<br />\n7. We need to stock up diagnostic test kits, mask and other PPE, quarantine areas, disinfectants, kaletra, ribavirin (low HCV oral dosing) and betaferon.<br />\n8. We must do everything now to delay or mitigate the epidemic till the increase of ambient temperature to 30 degree Celsius which hampers the environmental survival of this novel coronavirus.<br />\n<br />\nOur situation is NOT good. Need to see what happens in the next 14 days<br />\nWarmest regards.&quot;"},{"pid":"2828cd0b943f77966e859885d2ca9dc2922d172a","tid":1838540,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:19:45.000Z","msg":"拉到28號先罷工係無意義"},{"pid":"0a377ca321a1c313d40e0283c64dfe0b9fff7cdc","tid":1838540,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:09:01.000Z","msg":"<del>首階段為停止醫管局非緊急服務，在二月三日將採取惡劣天氣下之工作安排，平日於八號熱帶氣旋警告信號生效時無需上班的會員將會參與罷工，包括普通科門診職員及行政人員等；其他部門則按照部門內部就惡劣天氣所作出的當值安排（俗稱颱風更）上班，即假設二月三日已懸掛八號熱帶氣旋警告信號，如當日按照颱風更無需上班的會員則參與罷工。此階段為期一日，若醫管局於二月三日23:59分前依然未能就本會五大訴求提出切實解決方案，罷工計劃將立即進入第二階段。</del><br />\n<br />\n班on9拉到2月3日先罷工<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">根本到時一定已經爆發<br />\n有條件的立即離開香港<br />\n無條件的等死</span>"},{"pid":"065d9ca198c81bcfc6bba341d98bfca2ce0db108","tid":1838540,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c9668a04e860923bad639bbde42ba8e89ed3dfb","tid":1838540,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:14:34.000Z","msg":"醫護現在的方案係28號先開大會<ins>傾罷工</ins>,可能拉到<ins>2月中</ins>先罷到工<br />\n問題係現在一車車支那人湧去公院,到2月中若已經社區大爆發(大量香港人受感染),黃絲都唔會支持罷工<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係戰爭上掌握時期比萬全準備重要</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:11:20.000Z","msg":"28號, 返鄉香港人回港, 實好多中招, <br />\n個D客你邊有得罷? 香港人WOR"},{"pid":"cbdf0b6fdbe00dac6608778d928e3212d645fe9a","tid":1838540,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"065d9ca198c81bcfc6bba341d98bfca2ce0db108","tid":1838540,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c9668a04e860923bad639bbde42ba8e89ed3dfb","tid":1838540,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:14:34.000Z","msg":"醫護現在的方案係28號先開大會<ins>傾罷工</ins>,可能拉到<ins>2月中</ins>先罷到工<br />\n問題係現在一車車支那人湧去公院,到2月中若已經社區大爆發(大量香港人受感染),黃絲都唔會支持罷工<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係戰爭上掌握時期比萬全準備重要</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:11:20.000Z","msg":"28號, 返鄉香港人回港, 實好多中招, <br />\n個D客你邊有得罷? 香港人WOR"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:13:23.000Z","msg":"仲有班智障會員見係醫護工會決定盲目支持<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1842943/page/6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1842943/page/6</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n班工會膠人係話2月3日第一階段停工<br />\n<br />\n到時18區已經爆發"},{"pid":"ef6c2b38b1da15bb39aeea94460603162c44ad8f","tid":1838540,"uid":331973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:16:50.000Z","msg":"即日開始罷工，等政府回應，開始左罷工就會有其他人附和再同政府傾，而家同政府傾，佢點會理你。"},{"pid":"8ca939c2a29ea29787a24edd1526254f64a2bcfc","tid":1838540,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef6c2b38b1da15bb39aeea94460603162c44ad8f","tid":1838540,"uid":331973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:16:50.000Z","msg":"即日開始罷工，等政府回應，開始左罷工就會有其他人附和再同政府傾，而家同政府傾，佢點會理你。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:17:56.000Z","msg":"班on9話要守工會制度要跟程序,通知期"},{"pid":"2dd4d26a99b100a76cda6a48c6a7b0c0d665d41c","tid":1838540,"uid":331973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:20:51.000Z","msg":"玩程序，玩制度，政府最醒